Signed-off-by: Trond Myklebust <trond.myklebust@primarydata.com>
(compile-)Tested-by: Boris Ostrovsky <boris.ostrovsky@oracle.com>
Reviewed-by: Geert Uytterhoeven <geert@linux-m68k.org>
